      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCENIC SUNDARI (5) was out of the placings last time when sixth at Q Parklands (30.70) but scored four back at this track (25.35). Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Form from her last run is proving strong. Better than last start and worth following up. PACKHAM PUNCH (4) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at this track over 390m behind Golden Pharaoh (22.39) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. CASHED UP BETH (1) is boxed nicely on the inside. Last start finished 7th in a Grade 5 on April 15 over 366m at Capalaba behind Crickle Owl Vic beaten 6 lengths (20.25). Can hit the frame with the right run. MOJO BONE (2) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
